tal partners about usour teamportfoliomedia  eventscontact usinvestor login country exposure industry exposure clearwater capital partners portfolio consists primarily of public and private debt equity or other instruments issued by financially distressed or stressed enterprises in asian credit markets the firms investment strategy is focused on building diversified holdings of noncorrelated cashgenerating instruments that provide natural exits and are sourced from niche segments of the regions distressed market where borrowers have demonstrated an ability and willingness to pay creditors clearwaters goal in its strategy is to limit risk and volatility while maximizing current returns and identifying targeted upside potential in the firms portfolios this is accomplished through the firms investment philosophy a disciplined investment approach that draws on clearwaters indepth proprietary research and sophisticated portfolio management conducted by marketseasoned professionals  clearwater capital partners llcdisclaimer disclaimer  clearwater capital partners about usour teamportfoliomedia  eventscontact usinvestor login the information contained herein is provided for informational purposes only and may not be relied on as an offer to sell or a solicitation of an offer to buy an interest in any clearwater capital partners llc managed entity the information contained herein is confidential and may not be reproduced or redistributed without clearwaters prior written consent past performance is not an indication of future results  clearwater capital partners llcdisclaimer our team  clearwater capital partners about usour teamportfoliomedia  eventscontact usinvestor login partners robert petty managing partner and cofounder amit gupta partner and cofounder senior investment professionals senior business professionals senior advisor clearwater capital partners investment strategy represents the vision of its founding partners – robert petty and amit gupta – and each is in